#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
vector<int> v(15);
int bin(int n)
{
	int c=0,r;
	while(n!=0)
	{
		r=n%2;
		if(r)
			c++;
		n/=2;
	}
	return c;
}
int main()
{
	int i,t,ans,x;
	scanf("%d",&t);
	while(t--)
	{
		ans=0;
		for(i=0;i<15;i++)
		{
			scanf("%d",&(v[i]));
			ans=ans^v[i];
		}
		scanf("%d",&x);
		if(bin(ans)>x)
			printf("YES\n");
		else
			printf("NO\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
